name: Domino Sugars
description:
The Domino Sugars sign has graced the Baltimore city skyline for generations. 
This iconic landmark is a symbol of pride for Baltimore natives.
At night the light of the sign can be seen for miles,like the north star of our city, it's light guides us home. The sight of the sign fills my mind with home town pride and happy memories of my hero.
          Rest in peace
